  <div class="w-100 fn ph3 ph5-ns black avenir f3 cf">
    <h2 class="navy">Services</h2>
    <div class="mb2">
      <h4>Company culture &amp; HR process:</h4>
      <ul class="">
        <li class=" pb4 pb0-ns fn fl-ns w-50-ns pr3-ns">
          <em class="green">Policy analysis and development:</em><br><br> I’ll look through your current staff
          handbook, contracts, and policies to identify places where there may be
          hidden prejudices, work with your HR team to ensure your policies enable
          and protect your employees and have diversity at the center.
        </li>
        <li class=" pb4 pb0-ns fn fl-ns w-50-ns pl3-ns">
          <em class="green">Culture analysis and development:</em><br><br> I can analyse the organisation’s work culture by
          looking at employee satisfaction, the primary ways employees socialise with
          each other, and create an environment that makes sure employees are safe
          and are not only giving the most, but getting the most from work.
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="mb2">
      <h4 class="mt1-ns">Diverse recruitment &amp; hiring:</h4>
      <ul>
        <li class=" pb4 pb0-ns fn fl-ns w-50-ns pr3-ns">
          <em class="green">Job description analysis:</em><br><br> I can work with your organisation to ensure that your
          job descriptions and adverts are not biased and are as inviting as possible.
          This includes analysing your job description for keywords and phrases,
          ensuring that the qualifications are in line with the role, improving current job
          descriptions to be more inviting.
        </li>
        <li class=" pb4 pb0-ns fn fl-ns w-50-ns pl3-ns">
          <em class="green">Hiring process review:</em><br><br> I’ll be working with your organisation to improve the
          hiring process to ensure that the best candidates are not discriminated during
          the process. This includes analysing the interview and testing process to
          identify weaknesses, implementing the best practices for interview process for
          the organisation and potential employee, reviewing testing process and
          implementing best practices for code testing to ensure that applicants are
          given the best chance to succeed.
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>

