      <ul>
        <li class=" pb4 pb0-ns fn fl-ns w-third-ns pr3-ns">
          <em class="green">Company and team make up:</em><br><br> % of men, women, ethnic minorities, LGBTQIA,
          uni-educated, class background, ability &amp; the intersections of each e.g. % of
          white, heterosexual, able-bodied men in the tech team.
        </li>
        <li class=" pb4 pb0-ns fn fl-ns w-third-ns pl3-ns">
          <em class="green">Analysis of employee progression:</em><br><br> An audit and report of how often
          employees progress through the company, who progresses the most, who is
          least likely to progress.
        </li>
